---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Privacy Policy - CourseSpeak"
    description="How CourseSpeak collects and protects your data."
>
    <div
        style={{
            background: "#0b0d12",
            minHeight: "80vh",
            padding: "4rem 1rem",
            color: "#e2e8f0",
        }}
    >
        <div class="container" style={{ maxWidth: "800px", margin: "0 auto" }}>
            <h1
                style={{
                    fontSize: "2.5rem",
                    fontWeight: 800,
                    marginBottom: "2rem",
                    color: "#fff",
                }}
            >
                Privacy Policy
            </h1>

            <div class="prose" style={{ lineHeight: 1.7, color: "#cbd5e1" }}>
                <section style={{ marginBottom: "2rem" }}>
                    <h2
                        style={{
                            fontSize: "1.5rem",
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            color: "#fff",
                            marginBottom: "1rem",
                        }}
                    >
                        Data Collection
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        We collect minimal data to improve your experience. This
                        may include analytical data (cookies) to understand site
                        usage patterns.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section style={{ marginBottom: "2rem" }}>
                    <h2
                        style={{
                            fontSize: "1.5rem",
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            color: "#fff",
                            marginBottom: "1rem",
                        }}
                    >
                        Third-Party Links
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        Our site contains links to third-party websites (e.g.,
                        Udemy). We are not responsible for the privacy practices
                        of these external sites. We encourage you to read their
                        privacy policies.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section style={{ marginBottom: "2rem" }}>
                    <h2
                        style={{
                            fontSize: "1.5rem",
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            color: "#fff",
                            marginBottom: "1rem",
                        }}
                    >
                        Cookies
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any
                        time. However, this may affect some site functionality.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section
                    style={{
                        marginBottom: "2rem",
                        padding: "1.5rem",
                        background: "#1f2330",
                        borderRadius: "8px",
                    }}
                >
                    <h3
                        style={{
                            fontSize: "1.2rem",
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            color: "#fff",
                            marginBottom: "0.5rem",
                        }}
                    >
                        Privacy Concerns
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        If you have questions about your data, contact us at <a
                            href="mailto:privacy@coursespeak.com"
                            style={{ color: "#3b82f6" }}
                            >privacy@coursespeak.com</a
                        >.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
